Rules.InvariantScript:
ClearCollect(
    colDivisions,
    AddColumns(
        GroupBy(
            Filter(
                Wards,
                !('Title' in ForAll(
                    Filter(
                        'FTSU Ward Visits - Dev',
                        Created >= NotVisitedFromDate_dp.SelectedDate &&
                        Created <= NotVisitedToDate_dp.SelectedDate
                    ),
                    'Ward Area'.Value
                ))
            ),
         Division,     
          Gallery2    
        ),
        WardCount, CountRows(Wards)  
    )
)
